*Prevod* je prvi korak u učenju stranog jezika. (Translation is the first step in learning a foreign language.)

Ova knjiga ima *prevod* na više jezika. (This book has a translation into several languages.)

Ona je profesionalni *prevodilac*. (She is a professional translator.)

Njegov *prevod* je tačan i precizan. (His translation is accurate and precise.)

Ona radi *prevode* za strane kompanije. (She does translations for foreign companies.)